HNA Wants Discount on 20% NH Stake, Confidencial Says

-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 
2011-09-29T07:41:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/hna-wants-20-discount-on-nh-hoteles-stake-confidencial-reports.html
(Corrects to make clear that requested discount refers to
20 percent stake.)  China ’s HNA Group Co. is asking to
pay less than initially agreed for a 20 percent stake in Spanish
hotel chain  NH Hoteles SA (NHH) , El Confidencial  reported, citing
unidentified people familiar with the matter.  NH’s stock has fallen by 40 percent since the transaction
was announced in May, the financial news website said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Esteban Duarte in Madrid at 
 eduarterubia@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Martin at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net . 